  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start with a single branch on a flying island and a dream — becoming the greatest tree of them all.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each branch of the tree can grow new branches or leaves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can grow your tree in any shape and direction, but beware — new branches cost energy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growing leaves helps maintain energy balance and you need to be careful with it if you want to continue growing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reaching new heights unlocks new leaves you can use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some of the zones suppress your tree and you can't grow new parts inside them, but you can still grow through them and reach new heights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181350/extras/6730b2a283f99374cbe4b1720970e5a5.poster.avif?t=1730909647\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181350/extras/6730b2a283f99374cbe4b1720970e5a5.webm?t=1730909647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181350/extras/6730b2a283f99374cbe4b1720970e5a5.mp4?t=1730909647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Building and shaping your tree in any form you like.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Different atmospheric layers, types of leaves you can use, branches colors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Managing resources (energy and growth space).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Relaxing gameplay</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start with a single branch on a flying island and a dream — becoming the greatest tree of them all.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each branch of the tree can grow new branches or leaves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can grow your tree in any shape and direction, but beware — new branches cost energy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growing leaves helps maintain energy balance and you need to be careful with it if you want to continue growing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reaching new heights unlocks new leaves you can use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some of the zones suppress your tree and you can't grow new parts inside them, but you can still grow through them and reach new heights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181350/extras/6730b2a283f99374cbe4b1720970e5a5.poster.avif?t=1730909647\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181350/extras/6730b2a283f99374cbe4b1720970e5a5.webm?t=1730909647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181350/extras/6730b2a283f99374cbe4b1720970e5a5.mp4?t=1730909647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Building and shaping your tree in any form you like.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Different atmospheric layers, types of leaves you can use, branches colors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Managing resources (energy and growth space).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Relaxing gameplay</p></li></ul>",
